Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.58,0:00:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.25,0:00:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.79,0:00:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.90,0:00:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.11,0:00:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.91,0:00:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.19,0:01:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.63,0:01:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.30,0:01:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.94,0:01:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.64,0:01:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.40,0:01:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac175年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.90,0:01:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的領導者被暗殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.44,0:01:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部鋼彈被派往地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.77,0:01:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本應為了報復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.48,0:01:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但OZ在宇宙的行動並非支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.51,0:01:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於他們全面提出和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星認同OZ了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.26,0:01:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.62,0:01:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在支配地球和宇宙的進程中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.19,0:01:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈被視作叛軍\N的象徵給孤立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.73,0:02:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無家可歸的鋼彈和其駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.30,0:02:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在不斷轉變的時代裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.07,0:02:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以存在意義為賭注的繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.31,0:02:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒打中?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避過了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.42,0:02:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞，有另一個了解我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.79,0:02:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是關懷我\N擁有兩顆心靈的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行動是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.89,0:02:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我這行動也是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十三話\N[變回死神的迪歐]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓艙物的調整要慢慢來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.62,0:02:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，用燈照那裡的岩石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行過多次戰鬥卻沒有損毀呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.43,0:03:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有船接近這海域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛把這部鋼彈棄在海裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.10,0:03:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聲東擊西，而自己就飛上宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.01,0:03:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機動戰士潛水空母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ當然會來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是危險的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳不要擔心相信僱傭兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是前聯合深海部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大顯身手的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派西斯準備出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一時方向確認反射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是01
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!坎沙出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確認螺旋聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敵人機動戰士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.18,0:03:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坎沙部隊!快回答!坎沙部隊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然拋下鋼彈離去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有甚麼打算呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，這部機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會創造今後的時代啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是量產型也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用計較成本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙有無限的資源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想把宇宙衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變回本來的宇宙殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.55,0:05:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晚會讓他知道厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你運那東西去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你們偷了我們的技術後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解體了的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真榮幸呢，想不到變成廢鐵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.03,0:05:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也會引起你的興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.24,0:05:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說甚麼?\N我對那種東西沒興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點丟掉它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，技師長大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.31,0:05:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,製造比鋼彈更優良的機動戰士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了，別那樣催我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.06,0:05:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有太多事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.73,0:05:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然只剩下裝修啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙不是有討厭戰爭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨立思想嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在為何一定要拿起武器?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星只是實驗設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經是百年以前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了避免戰鬥，我們決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武裝起來也是迫不得已的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.56,0:06:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉‧普奧，前聯合軍少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是反OZ叛亂份子的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支持及指揮各地的秘密活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.70,0:06:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有情報說他們得到01和04
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推動OZ的羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.07,0:06:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是地球上最強大的組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那組織裡也有若干問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.95,0:06:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們想保護衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我們認同了OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋求更高更可靠的安全性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球繼續著武力鬥爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是從它的影響中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.96,0:06:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護自己而選擇的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球對抗OZ的人認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.80,0:07:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉住那班鋼彈技師的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.33,0:07:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是想把這世界\N變為極危險的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.64,0:07:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們收到報告說\N技師已經被處死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.21,0:07:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦是避免再次出現那種叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.14,0:07:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有力量就不能\N維持國家的尊嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的決定不會改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.12,0:07:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特大使，請你明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.09,0:07:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺了技師?不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種假情報才不得不最害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,物資和零件已經
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從各個工場衛星運來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到OZ協助的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經準備在月面工場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.48,0:07:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,量產最新型的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.58,0:07:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不用再害怕侵略的恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為特列斯統帥和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校的努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.19,0:07:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙才能迎接新時代的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虧你們說得出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩人會為你們帶來戰爭的恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.20,0:08:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以往衛星一直在屈辱的歷史裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.97,0:08:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不害怕令衛星站起來的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是希爾妲‧舒拜嘉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個衛星的志願兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的士兵嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也會批評
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個衛星的大部份學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報名擔任月面工場的守衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.69,0:08:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要知道行動才是信念的表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.22,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.73,0:08:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我也報名試試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次兵役檢查在一星期後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有意思就參加試試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請務必讓我參加啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我押去月面基地嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.95,0:09:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我做新型機的測試駕駛員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作新型機的目標吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ也認同你的膽色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.06,0:09:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ和其母體羅姆斐拉的戰略目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.23,0:09:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是令地球圈統一聯合崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.84,0:09:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到地球的支配權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.47,0:09:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何不幹脆支配衛星?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.98,0:09:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配毫無防備的衛星對OZ來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.65,0:09:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就等於扭斷嬰兒的手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.72,0:09:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他或許能理解啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.79,0:09:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯希望決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自以為是的衛星會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.42,0:09:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們和特列斯力量上的差距吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.03,0:09:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體快點準備上船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝，辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?找我有事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招募新志願兵在一星期後啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看一下那張報名表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這張很完美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這是偽造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里歐被搶走了!追!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.98,0:10:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要動!\N我不想在衛星內開砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.48,0:10:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃得掉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是破壞月面工場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但路程這樣就太遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.93,0:10:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不會手下留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫無實戰經驗的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警告也不會有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了衛星的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也為了衛星在戰鬥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標進入射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.96,0:11:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!我們為了衛星在戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們為何變成敵人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過我們不是敵人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是志願兵，發誓效忠OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有心理準備隨時犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.58,0:11:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的大無畏精神令我吃驚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.22,0:12:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐‧麥斯威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你是鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有心理準備隨時犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想被敵人同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳叫希爾妲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說的敵人誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.77,0:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星何時起變成\N戰爭中的組織?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前聯合從地球攻來時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.51,0:12:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑容從衛星的所有人面上消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了得回那笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑容回到衛星又如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.39,0:12:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家不是親自在拋掉笑容嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.89,0:12:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星何時起變得不正常?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的戰爭狀態影響到宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.53,0:12:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙已經不能再束手待斃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是宇宙的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.47,0:13:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真勇敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們載我去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.65,0:13:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裡審問你有關鋼彈的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的目的是破壞月面基地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.25,0:13:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何不當我是敵人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你得逞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恕我直言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以妳的力量根本不是我的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種傢伙竟然\N豁出性命和我對抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我覺得妳不顧後果的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和獨自挑戰地球的我很相似
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一定是傻瓜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.81,0:13:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士兵何時死去也不出奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.18,0:13:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的同伴今後會有多人犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們盡力走自己相信的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是那麼傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不能成為士兵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問到甚麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.63,0:14:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,班長，剛才的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威嚇射擊不是也可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.67,0:14:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命令說殺死叛亂份子也不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.01,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使自己人被牽連也一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.21,0:14:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希爾妲特士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.35,0:14:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但士兵要有心理準備隨時犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了任務啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,徵兵班長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即將到達月面基地上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我們的穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.96,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前往OZ的軍事設施移交俘虜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三引擎發生火警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.24,0:14:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像被人從內部炸毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.69,0:14:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎? 果然聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在要炸開艙門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想受傷就退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!迪歐!迪歐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的爆炸是甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?報告情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.23,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平衡器無效，很不利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.70,0:16:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到達月球了，很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死期到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我來說算做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來!快點了結我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.93,0:16:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但輸給機器令我有點生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.08,0:17:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!發出自己人的識別訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳會沒命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能發出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.36,0:17:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我已經不知道誰是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐，快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去做你想做的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希爾妲，妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.21,0:17:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也只是照自己意思盡力去做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.89,0:17:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，我現在救不了妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.03,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過吧，我有心理準備犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...希爾妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.81,0:18:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要白白送死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是呢，迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希爾妲!妳做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳先放下槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的行動非常有問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來在地底嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經通風系統就會直達工場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裡!捉住他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人入侵B6區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在追擊中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.39,0:18:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.32,0:18:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人企圖破壞機動戰士工場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?派守衛去地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止他入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.74,0:19:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.64,0:19:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.75,0:19:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.62,0:19:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四個也來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是殺死我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久沒見了，迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.99,0:19:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，是新機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐，你想駕駛它嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.83,0:19:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何時完成?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.00,0:19:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個月後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前\N你無論如何也要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.57,0:19:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，機會也會降臨你身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!這邊!快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.25,0:19:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐，快下決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以給人發現這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.05,0:19:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，快點開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能拜託你嗎?老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.29,0:20:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭的任務啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.47,0:20:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫出來會沒那麼痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但…我是男子漢呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.82,0:20:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙忘掉養育之恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然想殺死我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不會讓人\N阻礙我們的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務失敗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你破壞不了基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又殺不了博士他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別那樣說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…值得我來這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.78,0:20:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.58,0:21:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我的正在改良啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.46,0:21:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ看來會暫時讓我們活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得的機會\N你不要這麼快死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.60,0:21:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.90,0:21:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會那麼輕易就死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.90,0:21:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了衛星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.81,0:21:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會再次變成死神啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.31,0:21:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.88,0:21:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陪同匹斯克拉福特大使回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.38,0:21:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,護衛任務完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.42,0:21:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.69,0:21:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大使也明白\N宇宙決心的堅定了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為傑克斯‧馬吉斯又如何呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也是對時代有意見的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晚也會再有戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.73,0:21:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時再下結論吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.93,0:21:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無人能阻止歷史的洪流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.20,0:21:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是特列斯大人也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我把歷史移去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.58,0:22:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人的理想那裡就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.88,0:22:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此，我也能豁出性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.28,0:22:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要戰鬥，贏取未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏取特列斯大人的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.02,0:22:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有我的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.49,0:22:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.94,0:22:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.94,0:22:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.94,0:22:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.94,0:22:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.44,0:22:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.94,0:23:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.44,0:23:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.94,0:23:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.94,0:23:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.00,0:23:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切變得瘋狂的宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.04,0:23:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有毀滅一途嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.61,0:23:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常酷似鋼彈的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.51,0:23:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸續攻擊武裝起來的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.78,0:23:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦和希洛前去迎擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.85,0:23:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強力的新型機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.95,0:23:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但駕駛它的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.75,0:23:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充滿冰冷憤怒和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.19,0:23:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無限悲傷的卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.86,0:23:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第二十四話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.23,0:23:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名為Zero的鋼彈

